Hi everyone!
I'm Rohan Baijal, a sophomore in Electrical Engineering at IIT Kanpur. I'm interested Deep Learning and also like Julia. I found the Music Generation and NLP projects quite interesting. Could someone give me some pointers about what preliminary things I could work on related to this domain?
Thanks!
